      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving nature. This driver-spec example is paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity. The vehicle benefits from upgraded Bilstein dampers, providing enhanced damping control and sharper turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and delivers linear torque across the rev range. A robust, performance-oriented example for the purist who values mechanical substance over concours perfection.",
